00:01:47.659 --> 00:01:49.570
That shouldn't surprise you,

00:01:49.570 --> 00:01:52.052
because when you're calculating the mean,

00:01:52.052 --> 00:01:53.708
you're adding all the numbers up

00:01:53.708 --> 00:01:56.081
and you're dividing by
the numbers you have.

00:01:56.081 --> 00:01:58.235
If all the numbers are five more,

00:01:58.235 --> 00:01:59.890
